{"tid":827912,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"貓仔經常係我張被上面痾尿點算","createTime":"2018-09-19T09:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T08:57:37.000Z","uid":37213,"like":196,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"d2472b9f4a2f76578e85c90b978b8e40f19f9741","tid":827912,"uid":37213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T09:32:42.000Z","msg":"我本來已經有一隻貓3歲男仔，最近養多左隻女仔貓2個月大，自從放左佢出黎之後(隔離左2個星期)好鍾意同我一齊訓，但係呢2日朝早發現佢係我被上面痾尿，佢平時係識得去用貓砂，就係唔知點解有時要係被到去，我今日洗好左張被(完全消毒，噴埋清潔噴霧)之後一鋪好佢就黎料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 扎定個馬就去，我一見到就即刻抱起佢，然後噴到周圍都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又要洗被<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 究竟係咩原因會咁樣，定係有咩病？點樣教佢好？求指教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n附上主子圖一張<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/19/173133_138c997a9b5847ecddc53bef1e812f27.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F173133_138c997a9b5847ecddc53bef1e812f27.png&h=213939e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b82498b42c0cb019bf5aecc4079aee947bfd3b09","tid":827912,"uid":156121,"like":99,"dislike":0,"score":99,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T09:35:36.000Z","msg":"有冇兩個沙盤<br />\n試下換沙 或者係個盤有冇蓋 又可能佢唔鍾意個位<br />\n有冇都好<br />\n係你隔離去廁所通常係鍾意你 或者/同埋 個沙盤冇安全感"},{"pid":"1ad79a21a9e0a3bc6b840fd3fe263de046acfa61","tid":827912,"uid":39069,"like":5,"dislike":7,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T09:37:17.000Z","msg":"困籠先啦 霸地盤呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5afe9f8c17fd0c5fa12ae822868baaab7029b14","tid":827912,"uid":170334,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T09:39:37.000Z","msg":"我隻貓有排都係咁<br />\n換左貓砂就無事"},{"pid":"116b96920020df3f23d92aaf10d5fd5d33b1f919","tid":827912,"uid":37213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b82498b42c0cb019bf5aecc4079aee947bfd3b09","tid":827912,"uid":156121,"like":